name: Archangel Reading
description:
The Angels Are Here To Help  

Angels are currently appearing on Earth in record numbers at this critical time in the earth's evolution, to help us heal ourselves and the planet. They WANT us to get closer and connect with them, to learn how to communicate, heal and be guided by them, so that they can touch our own lives, and help us to help others. That’s why they’re here. If you’re reading this , maybe it’s time for you to take the next step in working more closely with your angels?

name: Burning Question -Path of The Soul Tarot Reading
description: Do you have a burning question or want to know what spirit wants you to know  . Burning Question is a 3 card reading exploring a single question which you want answered

name: Romance Angel Reading
description: This reading gives you an update on your love life, past present and future. The reading will answer a lot of questions concerning your love life and where it’s headed

name: Spirit Inspired Drawing
description:
How do I draw spiritual guides?
Using soft pastels, full of colour and love I include also typed information about your guide; I may get their name, nationality and always a channelled messages and guidance for you that they want you to know now.
A spirit guide comes  to me in a variety of ways, depending on the personality of the guide. Often some will show me images and then the rest of the drawing takes place. Other times I just start to draw and the being transforms onto the paper  Some guides are very fussy and have to have every detail perfect, others don’t really mind. I use all my senses to connect with your spirit guide, and through these perceptions I am  able to draw an impression of your spiritual guide.

The types of guides who may come through in your drawing can be 
Angels, Ascended Masters ,Healers, Shamans, everyday common people, power animals, children, male, female, various nationalities.

Our spirit guides want to help us and make them selves known so we realize and understand that we are not and never will be alone. We are always connected to the source, it is just that sometimes we forget, and our guides like to remind us.

A note of caution: Your spirit guide drawing will need to be handled carefully, and may need to be stored in a frame, to avoid smudging. It will be sprayed with a sealant and a layer of tissue paper to avoid as much smudging in the postal process. Details of how to care for your drawing will be included when posted.

name: The Power Animal Spread
description: This is a five card spread that covers your lifes journey, lessons to learn and provides insight into what you may need to do to be at peace and happy . The messages draw on ancient shamanic animal wisdom.

name: Three Card Animal Dreaming Reading
description: Scott Alexanders Animal Dreaming cards are one of my favourite decks to use. The three cards represents the immediate past, current situation and immediate outcome .

name: Ten Card Celtic Cross
description: The Celtic Cross is the most popular spread for tarot. It can be used to to answer questions  anout any topic.This spread of ten cards reveals the basis of your situation, the challenge, the past, the future,and the likely outcome.

name: Tarot Reading
description: Three card Angel Tarot reading which covers your immediate past, curret situation and immediate future.

name: Past Life Reading & Healing
description: The amount of details seen vary among readers. When I see a past life, I see it rather like a video. I am able to fast forward through the years and decades, pausing at certain time frames and focusing on important events. The key, however, is my ability to perceive the emotional content of the people involved. This is important because unresolved emotional issues that are carried from one life to another can be blocks for our current individual paths.

name: Reiki Healing Distant or in Person
description: Reiki is a non-invasive, gentle, yet powerful method of healing. Reiki energy, (often described as `universal life energy' or `spiritual energy') is accessed/channeled  by me during a treatment. It enhances the body’s natural healing ability and promotes wellbeing.

name: 30 min Medium Reading
description:
The option of selecting photo reading is just the same as a face to face reading. Il connect with spirit in the same way. With a photo reading I also have no time restraints to get all the information spirit is giving me due to having another client waiting. I would also like to add that as a medium I have no control over who comes through, any more than you would were you to call a telephone number picked out of the air. Sometimes there is a specific person you are hoping to receive a message from, however sometimes another spirit might have more pressing information to convey to you and they will be the one who comes forward. I am always grateful for whoever answers the call. Respect is of utmost importance whenever I am dealing with spirits
All I require for this reading is a photo of you and your first name.
